g6 8. Nc3 $1 Bg7 9. Qd2 $1 {This is the difference between 7.Nbd2 and 7.Be3!}
h6 (9... O-O $1 10. Bh6 Qe7 11. O-O $1 b5) 10. d4 $1 $36) (7... Bd6 8. Nbd2) (
7... Bc5 $5) 8. Nbd2 (8. Nc3 $5 O-O $1 9. O-O $1 Re8 10. Ne2 $1 c5 11. Ng3 Bf8
