19. Qd1 Rxe4 $1 20. Qb1 Re8 21. Qxh7 Rxh7 $15) 17... Ng6 18. Qf5 Bd6 19. b4 Qh6
$1 {[%cal Gg6h4] Black continues to fight for the initiative.} (19... Nf4 $5
20. Qxh7 Rxh7 $11 {, and Black recovers the pawn he sacrificed either on h3 or
on e4.}) 20. Qf3 (20. Nf3 $6 Nf4 {/\g6} 21. Bxf4 Bxf4 22. Re1 g6 23. Qa5 (23.
